c: 16
v: 56
t: "Ken (koros kinnuk) uma taamoomik tanim tuxxiq kee tukalak tu kak Aaxige waan numtinwwellittey yaqbudeeniy keenih necee rizqhik maglab kah haana kinni, usun teetit xayyoowaanamkeh, Yalli isil xiibitak diggah isin Qhiyaamah ayro diraabah yol ginnaasitak sugteenimik esserimetton keenik iyya"